common.profile

Class AlgorithmProfile

  • java.lang.Object
    • common.CObject
      • common.profile.ProfileObject
        • common.profile.AlgorithmProfile

  • public final class AlgorithmProfile
extends ProfileObject
    The AlgorithmProfile class is a class containing the configuration for an algorithm. It is the software representation of the algorithm configuration file.
    Author:
    Vincent Mirian
    Date:
    Oct 27, 2017
